{"tid":91182,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"講吓你父母對你做過最衰嘅嘢","createTime":"2017-01-22T16:11:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-23T02:51:38.000Z","uid":50582,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e7da18251e8bb38e7700668a574527ecdd1e1ab2","tid":91182,"uid":50582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T16:11:06.000Z","msg":"我先<br />\n平聲平氣叫佢唔好成日都咁閪語氣同人講嘢<br />\n跟住比佢打咗巴 話我乜鳩都斤斤計較<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dded4627f86488e39dcf6c3bbd67f68b9a63618","tid":91182,"uid":75389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T16:13:35.000Z","msg":"咩都係命令式。同佢地講道理就會嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e20689b27d68addd3e3897bda57b870c884f4e30","tid":91182,"uid":30972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T16:15:38.000Z","msg":"同佢地講道理等於冇大冇細<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"589639634a2a6012c131dc7b58e948d89718e8d0","tid":91182,"uid":75389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T16:19:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同佢地講道理等於冇大冇細<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n總有家庭係做得到好和和氣氣, 我都好羨慕呢啲"},{"pid":"8149000bdf36742208d4b728a62b28875fe460b2","tid":91182,"uid":30972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T16:29:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同佢地講道理等於冇大冇細<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n總有家庭係做得到好和和氣氣, 我都好羨慕呢啲</blockquote><br />\n係可以做到和和氣氣 但大前題係互相忍讓囉 一諗到佢地為我做左咁多野 唔過份就忍下算 希望屋企就算好嘈 都係一家人嘅笑聲而嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e1247134f1970ffb58c996cb84b8d9dda9fe317","tid":91182,"uid":56729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T16:57:52.000Z","msg":"成日話自己好開通好支持仔女<br />\n點知我一彈琴佢就話好嘈 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有D野好奇怪<br />\n識過有唔熟既女仔會鍾意聽我彈<br />\n但至親既人就永遠只會覺得係噪音<br />\n好難頂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e12fc7d5791b9118947b805761ddb20209b86a7","tid":91182,"uid":44775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T17:01:19.000Z","msg":"升中幫我簡左間男校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除左呢樣之外,父母真係幾錫我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b17794027089506dd6758292458ae644df5f0752","tid":91182,"uid":49741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T17:18:04.000Z","msg":"吾相信啊哥虐待我"},{"pid":"ca62a5d088120e313ee55714826adcc0c2cd95d2","tid":91182,"uid":22820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T17:39:17.000Z","msg":"諗住攞菜刀砍死我同我細佬然後再跳樓自殺<br />\n但俾我老母同姑媽叔叔制止咗"},{"pid":"aebecef150c7f9d6b93a40dda1d85243d032d0f3","tid":91182,"uid":22820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T17:39:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>吾相信啊哥虐待我</blockquote><br />\n吾你老母"},{"pid":"94e3e429e6538345e60b24314822d17381008095","tid":91182,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T17:41:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗住攞菜刀砍死我同我細佬然後再跳樓自殺<br />\n但俾我老母同姑媽叔叔制止咗</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f4eb841bacb991eaac1dbbb3aafafeb4cd23843","tid":91182,"uid":53775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T18:54:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗住攞菜刀砍死我同我細佬然後再跳樓自殺<br />\n但俾我老母同姑媽叔叔制止咗</blockquote><br />\n乖～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />已經過左去啦"},{"pid":"100652fc97179b31a8538e5ef896f2bc9e583987","tid":91182,"uid":2510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T20:59:56.000Z","msg":"細個成日唔比我食雪糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0437fd935f4e4ce8d78761d212a04c599bff7521","tid":91182,"uid":75389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T02:10:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同佢地講道理等於冇大冇細<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n總有家庭係做得到好和和氣氣, 我都好羨慕呢啲</blockquote><br />\n係可以做到和和氣氣 但大前題係互相忍讓囉 一諗到佢地為我做左咁多野 唔過份就忍下算 希望屋企就算好嘈 都係一家人嘅笑聲而嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係話佢地無為我做到啲咩 我都會想尊重同孝敬佢地 但畢竟條路將來係自己行 我想自己選擇 仆街都唔會喊"},{"pid":"709988839de9f0aeb23ff49d8287a6dd4b123e78","tid":91182,"uid":21461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T02:13:09.000Z","msg":"D 人成日話天下無不是之父母同成9日都話無論父母點都好, 都要孝順對佢地好<br />\n真係害人不淺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f88ac9cd7222907da041eb6404b9100736d8085e","tid":91182,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T02:51:38.000Z","msg":"生我出黎"}]}